summary: The hottest thing about that part of the new trailer, to me, isn't even that he's pinning him against the wall or that he's...
body:
The hottest thing about that part of the new trailer, to me, isn’t even that he’s pinning him against the wall or that he’s being rough with him. It’s the way David Tennant chose to do it.

He didn’t just push Michael into the wall. He put his whole fucking body into it. You don’t have to do that to pin someone down. A simple forearm across the neck/shoulders or tight grip of the lapels would do. You don’t have to press your whole torso against theirs and roll your hips into them.

Crowley didn’t have to do that to get Az’s attention. But I am so thankful he did.
